query: I need to report a scam that happened recently. It started with an SMS message that looked official. The message came from a number that seemed trustworthy, claiming there were some bills I needed to address. It asked me to verify something via a link they provided. The scam incident occurred on April 7, 2025. The SMS was from a number, +6591322047, claiming to be from DBS, stating that I had outstanding bills to settle. It directed me to a link for verification: https://secure-dbs-login.com/verify. The message requested me to verify my identity due to outstanding bills. I was directed to a site that looked like DBS's official page, where I ended up entering my card credentials for verification,  it was legitimate. I provided my card credentials for verification,  it was necessary to settle the outstanding bills. I didnt realize it was a scam until unauthorized transactions started happening. Yes, I entered my card credentials, which included my card number and expiry date. I didn't realize it was a phishing site. They made it look so similar to the actual bank's site, which is why I trusted it at the moment. No, I didn't have to enter my CVV or PIN specifically, just the card number and expiry date. I thought I was doing the right thing to verify my identity, but it all turned out to be fraudulent. I really wish I had noticed the signs earlier. query: I wanted to report a phishing scam I encountered. It started with an SMS that seemed legitimate. The incident occurred on April 7, 2025. I received the SMS on that date. Yes, the SMS requested that I verify my identity because there were outstanding bills. It provided a link that led me to a webpage that looked like the DBS official site, where I entered my card credentials. I thought it was real at the time. The URL provided in the SMS was https://secure-dbs-login.com/verify. There was no email address associated with the scam, just that SMS message. Yes, after clicking the link, I was led to the fake site where I provided my card details. Subsequently, it resulted in an unauthorized bank transfer of $225.90 to a CITIBANK account, specifically the account number 15594078. Yes, that's correct. The beneficiary bank was CITIBANK, and the account number is 15594078. It was really frustrating to realize what happened after I clicked the link and provided my details. I thought I was verifying something important. Yes, that's correct. The beneficiary bank was CITIBANK, and the account number is 15594078. It was really frustrating to realize what happened after I clicked the link and provided my details. I thought I was verifying something important.

query: Hello. I want to report a scam I encountered on Carousell. I came across a listing that seemed legitimate, but I was scammed after making a payment. Yes, the listing was for an iPhone 16 Pro Max. It looked good at first and the seller seemed responsive until I made the payment. The price was $1466.85 for the iPhone. The seller, using the moniker 'alexa83', insisted on full payment upfront, which I thought was normal. Now I realize that was a red flag. All communication was done through Carousell's messaging system. I didn't use any other platform, just Carousell. The moniker I encountered was 'alexa83'. I didn't get a profile link, but that was the name used for the listing and all interactions. The bank transfer was made on June 22, 2025, which was the same day I inquired about the iPhone. Yes, that sounds correct. I appreciate your assistance in reporting this scam. Thats all I recall. Yes, that sounds correct. I appreciate your assistance in reporting this scam. Thats all I recall.

query: Hello, I need to report a phishing scam that occurred recently. The scam started with an SMS message. I received an SMS from a number stating it was from DBS. It just said I had outstanding bills from DBS and included a link to verify my details: https://secure-dbs-login.com/verify.
